            "body": "before this change on the new tests, you can see the prompt being replaced instead of being inserted before\r\n\r\n```\r\nRUN      T18 prompt buffer prompt_appendbuf with multi-element list and singleline prompt: 5.30 ms FAIL\r\nExpected values to be equal.\r\nExpected:\r\n{ \"line1-append\", \"line2\", \"cmd: \" }\r\nActual:\r\n{ \"line1-append\", \"line2\" }\r\nstack traceback:\r\n\t.../Xtest_xdg/test/functional/legacy/prompt_buffer_spec.lua:1089: in function <.../Xtest_xdg/test/functional/legacy/prompt_buffer_spec.lua:1077>\r\nRUN      T19 prompt buffer prompt_appendbuf with multi-element list and multiline prompt: 6.46 ms FAIL\r\nExpected values to be equal.\r\nExpected:\r\n{ \"line1-append\", \"line2\", \"cmd: input1\", \"input2\" }\r\nActual:\r\n{ \"line1-append\", \"line2\", \"input2\" }\r\n```",
